# Network Fundamentals

## Original learning diagram

This is the first diagram I drew while learning the basics of computer networking.

It intentionally simplifies the concepts to reflect my understanding at the time.

### What this diagram illustrates

- A LAN (Local Area Network) is a group of connected devices.
- The Internet connects many LANs together.
- Devices communicate through their local network before reaching the Internet.

